<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        width: 80%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #FDDA0D;
      }
      .appointment-details {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .appointment-details p {
        margin: 5px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Hello <%= @user.first_name.capitalize %>!</h1>

      <p>
        We are pleased to confirm your appointment with the following details:
      </p>

      <div class="appointment-details">
        <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @appointment.description %></p>
        <p><strong>Start Time:</strong> <%= @appointment.start.strftime('%B %d, %Y %H:%M') %></p>
        <p><strong>End Time:</strong> <%= @appointment.end.strftime('%B %d, %Y %H:%M') %></p>
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> <%= @appointment.duration %> hours</p>
        <p><strong>Fee:</strong> â‚±<%= @appointment.fee %></p>
      </div>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or need to reschedule, please contact us at Booking-app.com
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you for choosing our services!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Booking-app Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
